item.description: BCO Examples A repository for BCO example flat files. Table of Contents: HCV1a - This BCO was developed with the Reproducibility and Interpretation use case in mind. This is the archetypal BCO example and is in the BCO Specification repository. glycosylation-sites-UniCarbKB - This BCO was developed with the Data integration use case in mind. The full repository is available here UVP - This BCO was developed with the Accountability use case in mind.
